{"tid":1940679,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港青總幹事裁員瓦解工會","createTime":"2020-03-24T02:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T03:49:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c27694fdf725d39a65436fbb8fc81606f97e0d05","tid":1940679,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:31:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200324/NGDFSVJ7TZHSSHC4JYLRYKRL4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200324%2FNGDFSVJ7TZHSSHC4JYLRYKRL4E%2F&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1uvO%2FPyVe1I8S2KINgfvOuE%3D&h=a4a185e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200324%2FNGDFSVJ7TZHSSHC4JYLRYKRL4E%2F&h=1004d69f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200324/NGDFSVJ7TZHSSHC4JYLRYKRL4E/</a><br />\n<br />\n港青總幹事裁員瓦解工會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200324/large/1584980567_5d4a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200324%2Flarge%2F1584980567_5d4a.gif&h=a071a780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n數名被解僱的港青員工在立法會議員陪同下，指控遭總幹事何慶濂（圓圖）政治打壓。張志華攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】社福機構香港基督教青年會（港青）近日以疫情導致財困為由，連炒約30名員工，當中兩人為工會籌委會成員，令原先擁有八人的工會未能符合工會最少七人的要求，一夜間瓦解。有員工質疑管理層借疫情進行政治打壓，大爆總幹事何慶濂為「藍絲」，不但力阻成立工會，又批評員工支持「暴亂」忘本。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：酒吧轟不公：食飯唔會播毒？<br />\n<br />\n「耶穌俾民主釘喺十字架」<br />\n<br />\n港青工會於本月12日收到職工會登記局確認登記成立工會。前工會籌委、被炒的社會服務部員工K小姐（化名）表示，工會成立翌日即遭解僱，限令10分鐘內收拾物品離開。她形容港青內部瀰漫「白色恐怖」，「都唔知仲有冇人夠膽入工會」，工會暫未有新籌委填補空缺。K憶述去年工會籌組，即遭管理層打壓。她指總幹事何慶濂去年12月與籌委會面時，曾批評工會旨在拉攏政治團體，要求停止成立工會。<br />\n<br />\n另一被炒員工H小姐亦指何曾公開表示社運影響港青旗下的酒店業務，形容「暴亂」不停止，「酒店冇錢賺，你估你哋做到社會服務咩？」，更指耶穌是被民主釘在十字架上殺死。立法會議員張超雄指港青流動資金高達1.7億元，裁員部門每月支出僅27.5萬元，質疑「明顯唔係錢嘅問題」。社福界議員邵家臻已去信社署要求跟進，惟社署以港青為非整筆過撥款機構為由拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁銘恩"},{"pid":"bdb3c3ae799d59b5bf73a9de480375156d0f027c","tid":1940679,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:32:49.000Z","msg":"基督教團體<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd2bc29f9a88a776d26a9ba9dd7e94d47344a86","tid":1940679,"uid":39586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:46:35.000Z","msg":"「耶穌俾民主釘喺十字架」<br />\n又一個亂解聖經嘅偽耶撚"},{"pid":"eea15b42b19fb1c4cc377818a3b7777f253c26cf","tid":1940679,"uid":161726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:48:30.000Z","msg":"所以你點解唔上大陸搞教會?<br />\n大陸幫耶穌拆十字架"},{"pid":"269251730ab4a1856aeb1d069a6043ff1a8a8ab8","tid":1940679,"uid":255637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次拆撚埋YMCA佢 講完"},{"pid":"76fa31084a34fd0732059f1b1bae65d51df2c56b","tid":1940679,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"冇去勞工處?"},{"pid":"6a1e6579b4c5e29b85e0f749edc7b500bc19703a","tid":1940679,"uid":39010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:59:59.000Z","msg":"拆你十字架都要奶共<br />\n耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5380d4a8eac42bd8ead1c8f3e597e16dfee3a66","tid":1940679,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fdd2bc29f9a88a776d26a9ba9dd7e94d47344a86","tid":1940679,"uid":39586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:46:35.000Z","msg":"「耶穌俾民主釘喺十字架」<br />\n又一個亂解聖經嘅偽耶撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:01:21.000Z","msg":"咁唔去支持希特拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b979bfc581b6fc264f88852f00741d82fe515494","tid":1940679,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"唔係俾民主出賣係俾位高權重的人出賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=